  src.groovy.au.org.emii.portal.FilterType

enum FilterType

Types of filters a layer can take. To add a new type: 1) Make a new value for the filtertype enumeration. Note that all possible values are stored as strings in the database. 2) Create an appropriate type in the Javascript, i.e., in web-app/js/portal/filter
